title: 2014 had the fewest alcohol-related fatalities on record in Alberta (Government of Alberta)
text: ( Source : Government of Alberta ) 2014 had the lowest number of alcohol-related fatalities ever recorded in Alberta . Compared to 2013 there were 15 per cent fewer alcohol-related fatalities and drinking drivers in fatal collisions decreased
